{
  "text": "Immunohistochemistry showed Kir6.1 immunoreactive protein in small pulmonary vessels. Besides arteries, veins can also contribute to total pulmonary vascular resistance [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , an effect that is dependent on age and species. In agreement to our data, Michelakis reported expression of Kir6.1 gene expression in pulmonary arteries and veins of rats [CITATION_4] . Taken together, expression of Kir6.1 is not restricted to systemic circulation but also can be found in lung vessels.",
